7235c2e46150cdcc2255b683cd7ab0d96b","tid":1201522,"uid":257996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed9fb3ce4777719a34b20d710218422e52fe1030","tid":1201522,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"講真我真係唔撚明<br />\n大陸係咁撚好你當初就唔好撚偷渡落香港啦<br />\n落得嚟香港講得廣東話就唔好再紅底奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係屋企講政治得嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人明我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"因為反送中，我都同屋企人嘈"},{"pid":"0bb035a379ef6044f3759eb8bf7956c794a1f65d","tid":1201522,"uid":181778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"167fa476581f91bd523121f7f4ba1c9edf5c98eb","tid":1201522,"uid":111372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"我係阿爺個代偷渡香港，父母係單程證落黎，結果就係偷渡個D好憎共產黨但同時又好憎國民黨、英國佬、美國佬，父母就好撚紅底奶共。<br />\n<br />\n結果全都部都係睇死抗爭個班"},{"pid":"72b7cb5048f1d9490aaac762f9b71834a3add842","tid":1201522,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d73e8325888f9500c9f5b2262534d62b1697de1","tid":1201522,"uid":138833,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日係度講以前有幾慘幾慘 無野食又比共產黨沒收哂啲資產 所以偷渡過嚟香港<br />\n但係而家又日日係度睇啲抗日片 高呼共產黨萬歲 日本仔正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全諗唔明白<br />\n同佢講親政治一定屌到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"係 真心見風使舵"},{"pid":"613d55dda2cbaf0084751d0e251502b821f6c985","tid":1201522,"uid":109224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c75bd11a61836baa5ddbe24718f36b6d2d17a49","tid":1201522,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"466ba3a308ee07e5104e43eff3b6b073707e3059","tid":1201522,"uid":236368,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:38:26.000Z","msg":"點解我老豆唔同，日日屌共產黨仲叫我出去遊行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"你果種十個都冇一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:09:55.000Z","msg":"我相信其實有唔少，當日見到好多家長帶細佬一齊全家遊行<br />\n咁樣身教本身係好嘅，但係啲靚仔淨係識扭計話好攰，全家焗住離隊，我想講1,030,000呢個數真係完全低估左"},{"pid":"1f714f6e0e99bbaf4fdc75a2b67ce99838a3a04e","tid":1201522,"uid":141033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e133aedcc19f2f54f9be3c3421b0d59761b46263","tid":1201522,"uid":26773,"like":273,"dislike":0,"score":273,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"個個講撚到自己好撚愛國<br />\n但係就因為當年無野食走黎香港<br />\n咁撚愛國就唔應該走落黎<br />\n食樹皮都要繼續愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"以前冇嘢食，咪唔愛國囉。呢十年大陸有野食有野玩，仲賣地有錢收，咪愛國囉。<br />\n<br />\n試吓中國嚟多次飢荒？佢哋妹下妹下都行出嚟反共呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f01cbf5d4463d95f4d24fc834cfe4d25482869f","tid":1201522,"uid":60510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"成班蝗子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd0f1d5bcdabd97386210953ebc08028ee7d70c","tid":1201522,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c627e628fb303e65b7eb793f425c8517159c3f85","tid":1201522,"uid":142144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"唔明  呀爺國民黨團長黎  老豆日日屌共產黨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"成個家族國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽完d老人家經歷過的野就明白同中共無可能共存，佢地唔會因為安分守己聽聽話話放過我地，一窮起上黎就會趕盡殺絕<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔想和理非，但和理非都係會死會受折磨，反正最後都係咁，點解唔比個機會自己掙扎下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd94f610d02333157e7454a1c3ed