22,"uid":238613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"我都唔明 成日覺得最應該反共嘅係佢地"},{"pid":"e2a5ccad5929a1b63382f52cdd35b61c6271be9b","tid":1201522,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"100%明白 <br />\n勸你慳返啖氣<br />\n嘈黎無結果"},{"pid":"7aa206b50c88bc6aed3768a8be346a3eb98fb575","tid":1201522,"uid":70916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1ddeed16314f3489c163ac2aa36c390f1c95af","tid":1201522,"uid":113183,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"阿公比人鬥地主 跪玻璃 坐監 之後放翻出黎<br />\n老母到依家仲不斷讚共產黨<br />\n都唔知佢斯德哥爾摩定人頭豬腦<br />\n成日話佔中搞搞震 影響啲人買野意慾 搞到經濟差<br />\n我中學讀liberal studies 果時已經係政治問題上開始同佢嘈到宜家10年之後<br />\n其實中間都唔想同佢講<br />\n因為佢嘅思維同弱智無分別<br />\n但有時佢口upup <br />\n真係聽到會火滾又會忍唔住回佢<br />\n但永遠只有佢啱 歪理講成真理<br />\n正常有腦嘅人都會覺得佢嘅言論痴線<br />\n佢仲話要返大陸住喎<br />\ncrazy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"快撚啲送佢返大陸啦 唔好認佢做老母"},{"pid":"3b2484d79cb4e35197ee2d7b4bd294d2c416347a","tid":1201522,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a45f3fdaedaa01059160268131b7ea93eea0a21","tid":1201522,"uid":238613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"我都唔明 成日覺得最應該反共嘅係佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"啱 唔折墮都唔偷渡啦"},{"pid":"bad7de3c6b72df89d17fa0aa7e92669d0ead273c","tid":1201522,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203706/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203706/page/1</a><br />\n大家可以睇下"},{"pid":"1e4d2b83e6097d654624f7aacbbbd5ea6c72cd70","tid":1201522,"uid":63303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed67d3eb2c9449c566dd055b4af76f6ba33bcd84","tid":1201522,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ab752b52645e892c6c5cab3cbdbb797741dd2566","tid":1201522,"uid":63303,"like":177,"dislike":0,"score":17